Breath of the Ancestor								KEY:Ninja Trick ~ Breath of the Ancestor					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:NinjaClassFeatures.SpecialAttack.Supernatural.NinjaTrick.NinjaTrickOnly																																																																																																																																																DESC:The ninja chooses one imperial dragon type (Forest, Sea, Sky, Sovereign, or Underworld; Pathfinder RPG Bestiary 3 92–103) when she gains this trick, and the choice can't be changed. She can use supplies similar to those used for ninja smoke bombs to produce an alchemical breath weapon that deals the same kind of damage as the selected dragon (piercing damage for forest dragons, fire for sea dragons, and so on).																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																															BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Breath of the Ancestor Type|1																																																SOURCEPAGE:p.22

Forest										KEY:Breath of the Ancestor ~ Forest						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:BreathOfTheAncestorType																																																																																																																																																								DESC:The ninja can use supplies similar to those used for ninja smoke bombs to produce an alchemical breath weapon that deals %1d6 piercing damage, with a Reflex (DC %2) save allowed for half damage. The breath weapon is a 15-foot cone. Using this ability is a standard action that expends 2 ki points, and once used it cannot be used again for 1d4 rounds.|SneakAttackDice|10+NinjaLVL/2+INT																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.22
Sea											KEY:Breath of the Ancestor ~ Sea						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:BreathOfTheAncestorType																																																																																																																																																								DESC:The ninja can use supplies similar to those used for ninja smoke bombs to produce an alchemical breath weapon that deals %1d6 fire damage, with a Reflex (DC %2) save allowed for half damage. The breath weapon is a 15-foot cone. Using this ability is a standard action that expends 2 ki points, and once used it cannot be used again for 1d4 rounds.|SneakAttackDice|10+NinjaLVL/2+INT																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.22
Sky											KEY:Breath of the Ancestor ~ Sky						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:BreathOfTheAncestorType																																																																																																																																																								DESC:The ninja can use supplies similar to those used for ninja smoke bombs to produce an alchemical breath weapon that deals %1d6 electricity damage, with a Reflex (DC %2) save allowed for half damage. The breath weapon is a 15-foot cone. Using this ability is a standard action that expends 2 ki points, and once used it cannot be used again for 1d4 rounds.|SneakAttackDice|10+NinjaLVL/2+INT																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.22
Sovereign										KEY:Breath of the Ancestor ~ Sovereign					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:BreathOfTheAncestorType																																																																																																																																																								DESC:The ninja can use supplies similar to those used for ninja smoke bombs to produce an alchemical breath weapon that deals %1d6 sonic damage, with a Reflex (DC %2) save allowed for half damage. The breath weapon is a 15-foot cone. Using this ability is a standard action that expends 2 ki points, and once used it cannot be used again for 1d4 rounds.|SneakAttackDice|10+NinjaLVL/2+INT																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.22
Underworld										KEY:Breath of the Ancestor ~ Underworld					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:BreathOfTheAncestorType																																																																																																																																																								DESC:The ninja can use supplies similar to those used for ninja smoke bombs to produce an alchemical breath weapon that deals %1d6 fire damage, with a Reflex (DC %2) save allowed for half damage. The breath weapon is a 30-foot line. Using this ability is a standard action that expends 2 ki points, and once used it cannot be used again for 1d4 rounds.|SneakAttackDice|10+NinjaLVL/2+INT																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																												SOURCEPAGE:p.22

