Agathiel										KEY:Vigilante Archetype ~ Agathiel						CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.VigilanteArchetype																																																															PRECLASS:1,Vigilante=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Vigilante Archetype ~ Agathiel],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Vigilante_Archetype_DualIdentity=True,Vigilante_Archetype_VigilanteTalent2=True,Vigilante_Archetype_VigilanteTalent4=True,Vigilante_Archetype_VigilanteTalent8=True,Vigilante_Archetype_VigilanteTalent12=True,Vigilante_Archetype_VigilanteTalent16=True]																											DESC:Agathiels surrender a portion of their immortal souls to Nirvana in exchange for a measure of animalistic might to aid them in their righteous crusades. This exchange is permanent, and each agathiel commits the rest of his mortal life to service of others and the constant thrum of wild instincts.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																		ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Agathiel ~ Immortal Commitment|PRECLASS:1,Vigilante=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Agathiel ~ Bestial Identity|PRECLASS:1,Vigilante=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Agathiel ~ Agathion Blessing|PRECLASS:1,Vigilante=2																																																																										COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.25																		FACT:Vigilante_Archetype_DualIdentity|true	FACT:Vigilante_Archetype_VigilanteTalent2|true	FACT:Vigilante_Archetype_VigilanteTalent4|true	FACT:Vigilante_Archetype_VigilanteTalent8|true	FACT:Vigilante_Archetype_VigilanteTalent12|true	FACT:Vigilante_Archetype_VigilanteTalent16|true	FACT:Vigilante_CF_VigilanteTalent2|true	FACT:Vigilante_CF_VigilanteTalent4|true	FACT:Vigilante_CF_VigilanteTalent8|true	FACT:Vigilante_CF_VigilanteTalent12|true	FACT:Vigilante_CF_VigilanteTalent16|true
Bellflower Harvester								KEY:Vigilante Archetype ~ Bellflower Harvester	NAMEISPI:YES	CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.VigilanteArchetype																																																															PRECLASS:1,Vigilante=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Vigilante Archetype ~ Bellflower Harvester],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Vigilante_Archetype_DualIdentity=True,Vigilante_Archetype_VigilanteSpecialization=True,Vigilante_Archetype_SocialTalent1=True,Vigilante_Archetype_VigilanteTalent6=True]																																			DESCISPI:YES	DESC:Bellflower harvesters are the front-line operatives of the secretive Bellflower Network, whose members infiltrate Chelish estates in the guise of servants and slaves, and tolerate a harsh life as they uncover secrets, gauge security, and send slaves on the first steps towards freedom.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Bellflower Harvester ~ Rebellious Identity|PRECLASS:1,Vigilante=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Bellflower Harvester ~ Bellflower Crop|PRECLASS:1,Vigilante=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Bellflower Harvester ~ Obsequious|PRECLASS:1,Vigilante=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Bellflower Harvester ~ Tend the Garden|PRECLASS:1,Vigilante=2																																																						COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.25																		FACT:Vigilante_Archetype_DualIdentity|true	FACT:Vigilante_Archetype_VigilanteSpecialization|true	FACT:Vigilante_Archetype_SocialTalent1|true	FACT:Vigilante_Archetype_VigilanteTalent6|true	FACT:Vigilante_CF_VigilanteSpecialization|true	FACT:Vigilante_CF_SocialTalent1|true	FACT:Vigilante_CF_VigilanteTalent6|true
Teisatsu										KEY:Vigilante Archetype ~ Teisatsu						CATEGORY:Archetype		TYPE:Archetype.VigilanteArchetype																																																															PRECLASS:1,Vigilante=1	PREMULT:1,[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Archetype,Vigilante Archetype ~ Teisatsu],[!PREFACT:1,ABILITIES,Vigilante_Archetype_WeaponProficiencies=True,Vigilante_Archetype_ShieldProficiency=True,Vigilante_Archetype_VigilanteSpecialization=True,Vigilante_Archetype_VigilanteTalent2=True,Vigilante_Archetype_VigilanteTalent=True]																													DESCISPI:YES	DESC:Teisatsu are specialized vigilantes who focus on infiltrating social scenes and high-society gatherings on behalf of the feuding lords of Minkai. Trained as assassins and spies, they cultivate a suite of personalities and study secret arts that hone their bodies into deadly weapons.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Teisatsu ~ Weapon and Armor Proficiency|PRECLASS:1,Vigilante=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Teisatsu ~ Infiltrator|PRECLASS:1,Vigilante=1	ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Teisatsu ~ Ki Pool|PRECLASS:1,Vigilante=2																																																																											COST:0	SOURCEPAGE:p.26																		FACT:Vigilante_Archetype_WeaponProficiencies|true	FACT:Vigilante_Archetype_ShieldProficiency|true	FACT:Vigilante_Archetype_VigilanteSpecialization|true	FACT:Vigilante_Archetype_VigilanteTalent2|true	FACT:Vigilante_Archetype_VigilanteTalent|true	FACT:Vigilante_CF_WeaponProficiencies|true	FACT:Vigilante_CF_ShieldProficiency|true	FACT:Vigilante_CF_VigilanteSpecialization|true	FACT:Vigilante_CF_VigilanteTalent2|true

#Agathiel
Immortal Commitment								KEY:Agathiel ~ Immortal Commitment						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Vigilante Class Features.AgathielClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																																															DESC:Becoming an agathiel commits a portion of the vigilante's soul to Nirvana, and in turn invests him with a portion of the plane's power. An agathiel's social and vigilante identity alignments must both be within one step of neutral good. If either of the agathiel's alignments moves outside this range (because of his own actions or magical manipulation), he gains 1 permanent negative level and loses the ability to assume his vigilante identity until both of his alignments are within one step of neutral good. This negative level cannot be overcome in any way (including by restoration spells) until the agathiel's alignment reverts.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.25
Bestial Identity									KEY:Agathiel ~ Bestial Identity						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Vigilante Class Features.AgathielClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																																															DESC:An agathiel's vigilante identity must invoke the appearance and behavior of a single Small or Medium creature of the animal type. The vigilante can attempt to appear to be a normal member of this animal type, but doing so imposes a –10 penalty on his Disguise check. The bonus provided by seamless guise still applies to the vigilante's attempts to appear to be an ordinary animal. Once the vigilante's animal form is selected, it cannot be changed.	DESC:When an agathiel assumes his vigilante identity, he physically transforms into an animal, though he always retains unusual traits that set him apart from ordinary animals, as if using beast shape I, except the vigilante gains no ability adjustments and can select only a single animal ability from those listed in the spell's description. His social identity remains his true form, and unlike with beast shape I, an agathiel can remain in his animal form indefinitely. The agathiel's vigilante identity is considered a polymorph effect, and while in his vigilante identity, the agathiel is immune to other polymorph effects. Unlike with normal polymorph effects, the agathiel's equipment does not meld into his form, and instead changes shape to fit his animal form and provides the same function, though any equipment requiring hands cannot be used until he returns to his social identity.|PRECLASS:1,Vigilante=4	DESC:When assuming his vigilante identity, the vigilante can select two abilities provided by beast shape I, or select a single ability provided by beast shape II.|PRECLASS:1,Vigilante=8|!PRECLASS:1,Vigilante=12	DESC:When assuming his vigilante identity, the vigilante can select two abilities provided by beast shape II, or a single ability provided by beast shape III.|PRECLASS:1,Vigilante=12|!PRECLASS:1,Vigilante=16	DESC:When assuming his vigilante identity, the vigilante can select three abilities provided by beast shape III, or a single ability provided by beast shape IV.|PRECLASS:1,Vigilante=16	DESC:This ability alters dual identity.																																																																																																																																																									SOURCEPAGE:p.25
Agathion Blessing									KEY:Agathiel ~ Agathion Blessing						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Vigilante Class Features.AgathielClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural																																																																																																																																															DESC:An agathiel gains Aspect of the Beast as a bonus feat while in his vigilante identity. If he selects the claws of the beast option,he can select a bite attack (1d8), a gore attack (1d8), or 2 slam attacks (1d4 each), as appropriate to his animal identity.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																									ABILITY:FEAT|VIRTUAL|Aspect of the Beast																																																																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.25

#Bellflower Harvester
Rebellious Identity								KEY:Bellflower Harvester ~ Rebellious Identity				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Vigilante Class Features.BellflowerHarvesterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																																																										DESCISPI:YES	DESC:A Bellflower harvester's vigilante identity must be within one step of chaotic good, and his social identity must appear to be a slave, servant, or other menial laborer. This alters dual identity.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																											SOURCEPAGE:p.25
Bellflower Crop									KEY:Bellflower Harvester ~ Bellflower Crop	NAMEISPI:YES	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Vigilante Class Features.BellflowerHarvesterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																																																										DESCISPI:YES	DESC:A Bellflower harvester can designate %1 allies as part of his Bellflower crop. Members of a Bellflower crop must remain within 30 feet of the Bellflower harvester in order to gain the benefits granted by a Bellflower harvester's other class abilities as detailed below; if they leave this range, the Bellflower harvester must designate these allies again for them to be included in his crop. When the Bellflower harvester uses the aid another action to grant a member of his Bellflower crop a bonus on an attack roll against an opponent, on a skill check, or to AC against an opponent's next attack, the bonus increases to +%2. This doesn't stack with the benefits of other feats or class features that improve the bonus he grants to an ally with aid another.|3+CHA|min(6,3+(VigilanteLVL+1)/6)																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																							SOURCEPAGE:p.25
Obsequious										KEY:Bellflower Harvester ~ Obsequious					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Vigilante Class Features.BellflowerHarvesterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																																																										DESCISPI:YES	DESC:A Bellflower harvester works hard to cultivate a social identity that plays off others' racist assumptions to deflect blame and excuse suspicious behavior, making him seem harmless or even a model servant. He can use the Bluff skill to deflect suspicion about his vigilante identity and activities (including use of vigilante talents when in his social identity) rather than Disguise, and gains a +%1 bonus on Bluff checks to do so.|min(6,2+(VigilanteLVL-1)/4)																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																															SOURCEPAGE:p.26
Tend the Garden									KEY:Bellflower Harvester ~ Tend the Garden				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Vigilante Class Features.BellflowerHarvesterClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																																																										DESCISPI:YES	DESC:A Bellflower harvester gains the ability to coordinate his Bellflower crop to improve their performance in battle. He gains Stealth Synergy as a bonus feat. As a standard action, a Bellflower harvester can grant any one teamwork feat he has to all members of his Bellflower crop who can see and hear him. Members of his Bellflower crop retain this feat for %1 rounds. A Bellflower harvester can share only one teamwork feat at a time in this manner.|min(4,1+(VigilanteLVL-2)/5)																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				ABILITY:FEAT|VIRTUAL|Stealth Synergy																																																																																																																		SOURCEPAGE:p.26

#Teisatsu
Weapon and Armor Proficiency							KEY:Teisatsu ~ Weapon and Armor Proficiency				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Vigilante Class Features.TeisatsuClassFeatures.SpecialQuality																																																																																																																																																	DESC:Teisatsu are proficient with all simple weapons, plus the kama, katana, kusarigama, nunchaku, sai, short sword, shortbow, shuriken, siangham, and wakizashi. They are proficient with light and medium armor, but not with shields.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																										AUTO:WEAPONPROF|Shortbow|Sword (Short)|Kama|Kusarigama (Sickle and Chain)|Nunchaku|Sai|Shuriken|Siangham|Wakizashi	ABILITY:FEAT|AUTOMATIC|Exotic Weapon Proficiency (Katana)	ABILITY:Internal|AUTOMATIC|Weapon Prof ~ Auto|Weapon Prof ~ Simple																																																																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.26
Infiltrator										KEY:Teisatsu ~ Infiltrator							CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Vigilante Class Features.TeisatsuClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																																																																DEFINE:VigilanteIsStalker|0											DESC:A teisatsu is required to choose stalker as his specialization. This alters vigilante specialization.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																			ABILITY:Special Ability|AUTOMATIC|Vigilante Specialization ~ Stalker																																																																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.26
Ki Pool										KEY:Teisatsu ~ Ki Pool								CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Vigilante Class Features.TeisatsuClassFeatures.SpecialQuality.Supernatural.Ki Pool																																																																																																																																														DESC:DESC:A teisatsu with this ability has a pool of %1 ki points, supernatural energy she can use to accomplish amazing feats. As long as she has at least 1 point in her ki pool, she treats any Acrobatics skill check made to jump as if she had a running start.|KiPoints	DESC:At 10th level, she also reduces the DC of Acrobatics skill checks made to jump by 1/2 (although she still cannot move farther than her speed allows).|PREVARGTEQ:VigilanteLVL,10	DESC:By spending 1 point from her ki pool, a teisatsu can make one additional attack at her highest attack bonus, but she can do so only when making a full attack. In addition, she can spend 1 point to increase her speed by 20 feet for 1 round. Finally, a teisatsu can spend 1 point from her ki pool to give herself a +4 insight bonus on Stealth checks for 1 round. Each of these powers is activated as a swift action. A teisatsu can gain additional powers that consume points from her ki pool by selecting certain teisatsu tricks. The ki pool is replenished each morning after 8 hours of rest or meditation; these hours do not need to be consecutive. The teisatsu can now use ki points from this pool to power the abilities of every class she possesses that grants a ki pool.																																																																																																																																																																						ABILITY:Internal|AUTOMATIC|Ki Pool Tracker																																																																																																					BONUS:VAR|KiPoolLVL|VigilanteLVL							SOURCEPAGE:p.26	ASPECT:KiPoints|Ki points

